{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As we were off the trains now, and we're in the-- on the-- on the railroad siding, we see German officers, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where they're dividing the men, or the able-bodied men and women from the either old people or women that had babies in their arms.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Very, very shortly after we disembarked, my father was shown to go to one side of the-- where it turned out to be the people that were kept for-- for work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- my mother is walking ahead of me with the youngest child in her arm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm walking behind her with one brother on each side holding on to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm in the middle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As I'm walking, I find-- I feel like a cane, a thing that has a round handle with a cane that you hold, a cane on my neck.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm being pulled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I just dropped my-- the hands of my two brothers on each side of me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he shows me to go to the-- to the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't say goodbye to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To this day, I-- I have [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a guilt conscious of not even saying goodbye.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I was confused.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the guy told me to move over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the last time I saw my mother and my siblings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, I am with a lot of people that are on the side, so-called, on the side that were going to live.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I knew my father was taken there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, I am on that side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I can't find my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'm all of-- I wasn't even 14 at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'm panicky.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
